	* src/GdbServer.cpp (GdbServer::rspUnknownPacket): New method.
	(GdbServer::rspClientRequest): Use rspUnknownPacket.  Remove
	handling of 'A', 'b', 'B', 'd', 'i', 'I', 'r', 'qCRC',
	'qGetTLSAddr', 'qL', 'qOffsets', 'qP' and 'qSymbol'.
