	(GdbServer::rspWriteAllRegs): Likewise.
	(GdbServer::rspReadMem): Likewise.
	(GdbServer::rspWriteMem): Likewise.
	(GdbServer::rspReadReg): Likewise.
	(GdbServer::rspWriteReg): Likewise.
