	ATDSP_VECTOR_SWI.  Add IVT_ENTRIES.  Replace ATDSP_NOP_INSTR by
	NOP_INSTR, ATDSP_BKPT_INSTR by BKPT_INSTR, ATDSP_TRAP_INSTR by
	TRAP_INSTR, ATDSP_BKPT_INSTLEN by BKPT_INSTLEN, ATDSP_TRAP_INSTLEN
